{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "914121ec-4c97-40ca-a451-d1390917a8d7",
    "name": "RaiPlay API",
    "description": "Reverse-engineered RaiPlay.it private API.\n\n## Auth Flow\n1. **Auth / Login** → auto-saves `x_auth_token`, `refresh_token`, `ua`\n2. When JWT expires → **Auth / Token Check (Refresh)**\n\n## Environment Variables\n| Variable | Value | Notes |\n|---|---|---|\n| `base_url` | `https://www.raiplay.it` | |\n| `domain_api_key` | `arSgRtwasD324SaA` | Static frontend key |\n| `email` | your email | |\n| `password` | your password | |\n| `x_auth_token` | *(auto)* | Set by Login test script |\n| `refresh_token` | *(auto)* | Set by Login test script |\n| `ua` | *(auto)* | Set by Login test script |\n| `search_term` | e.g. `Rocco Schiavone` | |\n| `date_from` | e.g. `05-05-2026` | DD-MM-YYYY |\n| `date_to` | e.g. `06-05-2026` | DD-MM-YYYY |\n| `timestamp` | ISO timestamp | For activity log |\n\n## Microservices\n- `raisso-service` — auth/SSO\n- `token-service` — anonymous tokens & geolocation\n- `raiplay-search-service` — full-text search\n- `raiplay-su-service` — user profile, seeks, favourites, play state\n- `prediction-service` — personalisation, recommendations, expiry\n\n## Known quirks\n- `domainapikey` header must be **all lowercase** on authenticated endpoints\n- Login response uses `authorization` field (not `jwt`) for the JWT\n- msearch uses static `templateIn`/`templateOut` IDs — do not change them",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
