            "description": "Primary full-text search used by the UI.\n\nKey params:\n- `param`: the search query string\n- `templateIn` / `templateOut`: static template IDs that define the query/response shape (do not change)\n- `size`: max results (default 48)\n- `additionalSize`: extra results for carousels (default 27)\n- `onlyVideoQuery`: true to restrict to videos only\n- `onlyProgramsQuery`: true to restrict to programs/series only\n- `from`: pagination offset",
